---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Services | Bosker Excavating & Trucking" description="Full-service excavation, trucking, grading, retaining walls, driveways, septic, and site work across Harbor Springs and Northern Michigan.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>Comprehensive excavation, trucking, and site work solutions for residential, commercial, and rural properties throughout Northern Michigan.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="service-detail" id="excavation">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">01</span>
            <h2>Excavation</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Whether you're building a new home, adding an addition, or developing commercial property, our excavation services lay the groundwork for success. We have the experience and equipment to handle any scale of dig.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Foundation and basement excavation</li>
            <li>Trench digging for utilities and footings</li>
            <li>Pond and water feature excavation</li>
            <li>Roadway and driveway excavation</li>
            <li>Retaining wall preparation</li>
            <li>General earthmoving</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9874;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="site-prep">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">02</span>
            <h2>Site Preparation &amp; Land Clearing</h2>
          </div>
          <p>We transform raw land into build-ready sites. From clearing brush to stripping topsoil and rough grading, we get your property ready for whatever comes next — fast and clean.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Land clearing and grubbing</li>
            <li>Brush clearing</li>
            <li>Debris removal and hauling</li>
            <li>Topsoil stripping and stockpiling</li>
            <li>Rough grading and leveling</li>
            <li>Access road construction</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9041;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="grading">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">03</span>
            <h2>Grading &amp; Drainage</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Proper grading and drainage protect your home and property for decades. We ensure water flows away from structures, your yard drains correctly, and you don't end up with a wet basement or flooded driveway.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Finish grading for new construction</li>
            <li>Yard regrading and reshaping</li>
            <li>French drains and curtain drains</li>
            <li>Stormwater management solutions</li>
            <li>Driveway grading and maintenance</li>
            <li>Culvert installation and replacement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9951;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="retaining-walls">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">04</span>
            <h2>Retaining Walls</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Northern Michigan's hilly terrain often demands a solid retaining wall. We build beautiful, durable boulder and fieldstone retaining walls that solve grade problems while looking natural and fitting the landscape.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Boulder and fieldstone retaining walls</li>
            <li>Large-scale grade change solutions</li>
            <li>New construction site walls</li>
            <li>Erosion control walls</li>
            <li>Decorative and functional designs</li>
            <li>Backfill and drainage integration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9776;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="driveways">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">05</span>
            <h2>Driveways</h2>
          </div>
          <p>A properly installed gravel driveway starts with solid prep work underneath. We grade the base correctly, install proper drainage, and deliver quality aggregate so your driveway lasts.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>New gravel driveway installation</li>
            <li>Driveway grading and shaping</li>
            <li>Culvert and drainage installation</li>
            <li>Gravel delivery and spreading</li>
            <li>Existing driveway repair and regrading</li>
            <li>Turnaround and parking area construction</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9660;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="trucking">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">06</span>
            <h2>Trucking &amp; Hauling</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Our dump truck fleet handles deliveries and removals of all kinds. Need gravel delivered? Debris hauled out? We move material efficiently and get it where it needs to go.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Gravel, sand, and crushed stone delivery</li>
            <li>Topsoil and fill dirt hauling</li>
            <li>Debris and spoil removal</li>
            <li>Aggregate and material transport</li>
            <li>Brush and debris hauling</li>
            <li>Snow removal services</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9931;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="septic">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">07</span>
            <h2>Septic Systems</h2>
          </div>
          <p>We install and repair septic systems that comply with Emmet County and local health department regulations. From new installations to replacing aging systems, we handle it properly and see it through to inspection.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>New septic system installation</li>
            <li>Septic system replacement and repair</li>
            <li>Drain field installation</li>
            <li>Septic inspections and evaluations</li>
            <li>Permit coordination with local authorities</li>
            <li>Mound and conventional systems</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#8853;</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail" id="demolition">
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <div class="sd-header">
            <span class="sd-num">08</span>
            <h2>Demolition</h2>
          </div>
          <p>When something needs to come down before something new can go up, our demolition services get the job done safely, efficiently, and with full debris removal.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Building and structure demolition</li>
            <li>Concrete and asphalt removal</li>
            <li>Foundation removal</li>
            <li>Interior and selective demolition</li>
            <li>Debris cleanup and hauling</li>
            <li>Site clearing post-demolition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-icon">&#9715;</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Need a Quote?</h2>
      <p>Contact us for a free, no-obligation estimate on your project. We'll come take a look and give you a straight answer.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="tel:+12314993784" class="btn btn-dark">Call (231) 499-3784</a>
        <a href={`${base}contact/`} class="btn btn-outline-cta">Send Us a Message</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Service Details */
  .service-detail {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .service-detail:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .sd-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sd-num {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .service-detail h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .service-detail p {
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .service-detail ul {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.4rem 1rem;
  }

  .service-detail li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .service-detail li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-detail-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-detail {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .service-detail-icon { display: none; }
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-banner {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .cta-banner p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 550px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-dark {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-white);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-dark:hover {
    background: #333;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-outline-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    background: transparent;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-white);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
